1. A double blind clinical trial was conducted.
2. The trial involved 49 patients.
3. All the patients had type 2 diabetes.
4. The patients had different degrees of neuropathy.
5. The patients were evaluated in two groups.
6. One group was given ANGIPARSTM.
7. The other group was given a placebo.
